{
  "stem": "22892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would have liked to do that myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wanted that, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was just-- at that time, I think I was about 14 or 15.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they just didn't-- but-- he was-- he was taken into the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's the-- he's the one that survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He joined some partisans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did-- but he-- all he could see was just taking revenge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted to do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was such a nice guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moishe was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pressman was his last name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just a nice guy, good-looking kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] So he, he joined the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a picture from him, and a letter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a little letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got that-- that was somewhere in the beginning of '45.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] February or something like that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] March.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- and the war was over in May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Rowne, finally, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yeah, that was in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was already-- you know, that was-- the Russians were already there in that city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was-- I felt, like, free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they bombed-- I, I stayed with a bunch of partisans in a house, where there was a shelter in a house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they were doing some bombing-- Rowne was a pretty good-sized city, maybe about 100,000.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were right near a bank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were bombarding the bank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germans would bombard at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody was running to the basement, people from other houses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the only one in bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, they're crazy, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they get killed-- they'll get killed there, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How about--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
